The impact of AI technology on the content industry can be divided into the following five aspects:

1. The application and use of AI technology in various fields of content industry;

2. The application and use of AI technology in traditional content industry;

3. The impact of AI technology on the development of content industry;

4. The impact of AI technology on the development of content consumption;

5. The impact of AI technology on the development of content production.
